## 12. Errors & Edge States

```text
12.1 Offline Mode              12.2 API Error                 12.3 Perms Recovery            12.4 Session Recover
+----------------------+       +----------------------+       +----------------------+       +----------------------+
|                      |       |                      |       |                      |       |                      |
|      (Cloud/)        |       |    /!\ ERROR /!\     |       |    ( Settings )      |       |      ( PAUSE )       |
|                      |       |                      |       |       ( Gear )       |       |                      |
|   No Connection      |       |   System Glitch      |       |                      |       |    Session Found     |
|                      |       |                      |       |   Camera Denied      |       |                      |
|    Everything        |       |  We're having        |       |                      |       | +------------------+ |
|    is frozen.        |       |  trouble connecting  |       | 1. Open Settings     |       | | Snapshot of      | |
|                      |       |  to the brain.       |       | 2. Tap TrueStep      |       | | last step...     | |
|                      |       |                      |       | 3. Toggle Camera     |       | +------------------+ |
| [ View Downloads ]   |       | [ TRY AGAIN ]        |       |                      |       |                      |
|                      |       |                      |       | [ OPEN SETTINGS ]    |       | [ RESUME ]           |
|      (Retry)         |       |                      |       |                      |       | ( Discard )          |
+----------------------+       +----------------------+       +----------------------+       +----------------------+
```